ラと輝きを放ち、贈られたあの子もきっと喜んでくれる――そう思うと笑みがこぼれるのだった。\",\"en\":\"A reindeer that prepares for Christmas, smiling at the thought of the joy the dazzling, neatly-wrapped presents will surely bring the children.\",\"ko\":\"크리스마스를 위해 루돌프는 준비를 시작한다. 포장된 선물은 하나같이 반짝반짝 빛나니까 선물을 받은 그 아이도 분명 기뻐하겠지―― 그렇게 생각하니 얼굴에 미소가 번진다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"聖誕節將至，馴鹿開始進行準備。每個包裝好的禮物，都散發出閃亮的光芒。那孩子收到禮物一定也會很高興──馴鹿這麼想，就不禁露出微笑。\"},\"published_at\":1545116400,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":0,\"role_index\":11050,\"trait_id\":0,\"win_sequence_id\":456,\"_id_\":1010005},\"1010006\":{\"attack_type\":2,\"attribute_id\":1,\"auto_skill1_id\":10078,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":1,\"auto_skill2_id\":20023,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":2,\"auto_skill3_id\":10074,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":1,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":168,\"base_atk\":177,\"base_hp\":942,\"base_mdef\":68,\"base_pdef\":68,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":101,\"command_skill1_id\":950,\"command_skill2_id\":951,\"command_skill3_id\":952,\"command_unique_skill_id\":953,\"confusion_skill_id\":954,\"cost\":12,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":2770,\"delta_atk\":2930,\"delta_hp\":31030,\"delta_mdef\":1120,\"delta_pdef\":1130,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"高いACTパワーを持つ。自身に必中を付与するクライマックスACTで敵役を退場に追い込む。イベント「名探偵華恋の事件簿」でユニット全体の能力を向上させる。\",\"en\":\"High Act Power. Gives Perfect Aim to self and heavily damages an enemy with her Climax Act. Boosts the capabilities of the entire unit in Detective Karen on the Case event.\",\"ko\":\"높은 ACT 파워를 가졌다. 자신에게 백발백중을 부여하는 클라이맥스 ACT로 악역을 퇴장으로 몰아넣는다. 이벤트 「명탐정 카렌의 사건기록」에서 유닛 전체의 능력을 향상시킨다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"擁有很高的ACT力量，以及能賦予自己必中的CLIMAX ACT，能逼迫敵方迅速退場。在活動「名偵探華戀事件簿」中能夠提升團隊全體的能力。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":1010006,\"dress_type\":0,\"entry_skill_id\":0,\"eva\":0,\"friendship10_reward_adventure_id\":3010100061,\"friendship15_levelup_adventure_id\":3110100061,\"friendship25_reward_adventure_id\":3010100062,\"friendship30_levelup_adventure_id\":3110100062,\"friendship_pattern_id\":121,\"get_message\":{\"ja\":\"この名探偵に解けない謎はないっ！\",\"en\":\"There's no mystery this detective can't solve!\",\"ko\":\"이 명탐정에게 풀 수 없는 수수께끼는 없어!\",\"zh_hant\":\"沒有我這個名偵探不能解決的謎團！\"},\"get_voice\":\"v21010002_004\",\"growth_board1_id\":12201101,\"growth_board2_id\":12201201,\"growth_board3_id\":12201301,\"growth_board4_id\":12201401,\"growth_board5_id\":12201501,\"growth_board6_id\":12201601,\"growth_board7_id\":12201701,\"growth_board8_id\":12201801,\"growth_board9_id\":12201901,\"hit\":0,\"model_id\":1010006,\"name\":{\"ja\":\"シャーロック・ホームズ\",\"en\":\"Sherlock Holmes\",\"ko\":\"셜록 홈즈\",\"zh_hant\":\"夏洛克福爾摩斯\"},\"obtain_route_flags\":0,\"party_skill_id\":36,\"party_skill_level_id\":2,\"party_skill_type\":5,\"personality_id\":1,\"profile\":{\"ja\":\"シャーロック・ホームズは、ベイカー街221Bに住む天才的な観察眼と推理力を持つ探偵だ。謎が彼を呼ぶのか、彼が謎を呼ぶのか……多くの事件を解決し、いつしか名探偵と呼ばれるようになっていた。\",\"en\":\"Sherlock Holmes is a genius detective with cunning wit and powers of deduction who lives at 221B Baker Street. Mysteries seem to appear wherever he goes, and with how many he's solved, it's no mystery why he became so famous.\",\"ko\":\"셜록 홈즈는 베이커 가 221B에 사는 천재적인 관찰력과 추리력을 가진 탐정이다. 수수께끼가 그를 부르는 것인지 그가 수수께끼를 부르는 것인지... 많은 사건을 해결하고 어느샌가 명탐정이라 불리게 되었다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"住在貝克街221B的夏洛克福爾摩斯，是名擁有天才般的觀察力與推裡能力的偵探。究竟是謎團喚來此人，還是此人喚來謎團……解決了無數的事件的福爾摩斯，不知從何時開始已被稱作為名偵探。\"},\"published_at\":1556175600,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":24050,\"trait_id\":32,\"win_sequence_id\":670,\"_id_\":1010006},\"1010007\":{\"attack_type\":1,\"attribute_id\":5,\"auto_skill1_id\":10011,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":1,\"auto_skill2_id\":20023,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":2,\"auto_skill3_id\":20024,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":2,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":