ンス期を代表する芸術家。探究心と独創性を兼ね備えた天才で、芸術だけでなく音楽、数学、天文学など様々な分野に業績を残し、後世の芸術家へ多大な影響を与えた。\",\"en\":\"The representative artist of the Italian Renaissance. A genius with both curiosity and creativity, leaving behind achievements not only in the arts, but also music, mathematics, astronomy and various other fields — a great influence to future generations of artists.\",\"ko\":\"이탈리아의 르네상스 시대를 대표하는 예술가. 탐구심과 독창성을 겸비한 천재로 예술뿐만 아니라 음악, 수학, 천문학 등 다양한 분야에 업적을 남기고 후세의 예술가에게 큰 영향을 끼쳤다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"義大利文藝復興時期的代表藝術家，兼具好奇心與創造力的天才。除了藝術方面之外，在音樂、數學、天文學等多樣的領域都有顯著的成就，對後世藝術家有著莫大的影響。\"},\"published_at\":1567666800,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":32050,\"trait_id\":36,\"win_sequence_id\":935,\"_id_\":1010007},\"1010008\":{\"attack_type\":1,\"attribute_id\":5,\"auto_skill1_id\":20023,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":2,\"auto_skill2_id\":10021,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":1,\"auto_skill3_id\":10082,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":1,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":179,\"base_atk\":178,\"base_hp\":955,\"base_mdef\":78,\"base_pdef\":90,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":101,\"command_skill1_id\":1463,\"command_skill2_id\":1464,\"command_skill3_id\":1465,\"command_unique_skill_id\":1466,\"confusion_skill_id\":1467,\"cost\":12,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":2950,\"delta_atk\":2970,\"delta_hp\":29240,\"delta_mdef\":1000,\"delta_pdef\":1000,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"高いACTパワーを持ち、ACT3で後ろから3人の敵役に大ダメージを与えることができ、クライマックスACTでは一定確率でスタンを付与することができる。\",\"en\":\"Possesses high Act Power. Her Act deals high damage to 3 rear enemies and her Climax Act has a chance to inflict Stun.\",\"ko\":\"높은 ACT 파워를 갖고 있으며 ACT3으로 뒤에서부터 3명에게 큰 대미지를 가할 수 있고 클라이맥스 ACT로는 일정 확률로 스턴을 부여할 수 있다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"擁有很高的ACT力量，可用ACT3來給予後方的3名敵人強大的傷害，CLIMAX ACT還可以一定機率對敵人造成暈眩。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":1010008,\"dress_type\":0,\"