01,\"growth_board5_id\":12102501,\"growth_board6_id\":12102601,\"growth_board7_id\":12102701,\"growth_board8_id\":12102801,\"growth_board9_id\":12102901,\"hit\":0,\"model_id\":1020004,\"name\":{\"ja\":\"塔\",\"en\":\"Tower\",\"ko\":\"탑\",\"zh_hant\":\"塔\"},\"obtain_route_flags\":1,\"party_skill_id\":154,\"party_skill_level_id\":2,\"party_skill_type\":5,\"personality_id\":2,\"profile\":{\"ja\":\"『塔』――それは地上より打ち上げられた宇宙船の機械知性。『星の少女』を月に送り届ける最中、船は攻撃を受けて燃え上がる。生と死のはざま、炎の奥で『塔』はある決断をくだす。\\n――『劇フェス』戯曲・第五幕より\",\"en\":\"The \\\"Tower\\\" – a machine intelligence inhabiting a spaceship shot from Earth. Tasked with delivering the 'Star Girl' to the Moon, the ship is hit and bursts into flames. In that moment amid the flames, the \\\"Tower\\\" makes a decision. From \\\"Performance Festival\\\" Play - Act 5.\",\"ko\":\"[탑]―― 그것은 지상에서 발사된 우주선의 기계지성이다. [별의 소녀]를 달에 보내던 중, 우주선은 공격을 받고 불타오른다. 생과 사의 갈림길, 불꽃 속에서 [탑]은 어떤 결단을 내린다.\\n――[극페스] 희곡・제5막에서\",\"zh_hant\":\"『塔』――那是從地上發射出的宇宙船之機械知性。在運送『星之少女』前往月亮時，由於艦體受到攻擊而燃燒。在熊熊烈火的生死之隙中，『塔』做出了某個決定。\\n――取自『戲劇慶典』戲碼・第五幕\"},\"published_at\":1604041200,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":21010,\"trait_id\":55,\"win_sequence_id\":1871,\"_id_\":1020004},\"1020005\":{\"attack_type\":2,\"attribute_id\":5,\"auto_skill1_id\":10019,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":1,\"auto_skill2_id\":20023,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":2,\"auto_skill3_id\":10078,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":1,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":176,\"base_atk\":171,\"base_hp\":1061,\"base_mdef\":69,\"base_pdef\":68,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":102,\"command_skill1_id\":733,\"command_skill2_id\":734,\"command_skill3_id\":735,\"command_unique_skill_id\":736,\"confusion_skill_id\":737,\"cost\":12,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":2910,\"delta_atk\":2820,\"delta_hp\":34980,\"delta_mdef\":1140,\"delta_pdef\":1130,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"バランス良いステータス。敵役全体を対象とするACTを複数持つ。クライマックスACTで敵役全体に被ダメージを増幅させる「刻印」を付与することができる。\",\"en\":\"Has good, balanced stats. Possesses multiple Acts that hit all enemies. Her Climax Act inflicts Marked on all enemies, causing them to take increased damage.\",\"ko\":\"밸런스가 좋은 스테이터스. 악역 전체를 대상으로 하는 ACT를 여럿 가졌다. 클라이맥스 ACT로 악역 전체가 받는 대미지를 증폭시키는 「각인」을 부여할 수 있다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"擁有絕佳平衡的能力值，並有複數個以敵方全體為對象的ACT。CLIMAX ACT可以對敵方全體賦予增加其所受傷害的「刻印」狀態。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":1020005,\"dress_type\":0,\"entry_skill_id\":0,\"eva\":0,\"friendship10_reward_adventure_id\":3010200051,\"friendship15_levelup_adventure_id\":3110200051,\"friendship25_reward_adventure_id\":3010200052,\"friendship30_levelup_adventure_id\":3110200052,\"friendship_pattern_id\":135,\"get_message\":{\"ja\":\"太陽神、アマテラス\\n――誰よりも、光り輝く神様\",\"en\":\"Amaterasu, goddess of the sun, shines brighter than anyone!\",\"ko\":\"태양신, 아마테라스.\\n――누구보다도 찬란히 빛나는 신.\",\"zh_hant\":\"太陽神…天照大神\\n──世上最光輝眩目的神明。\"},\"get_voice\":\"v21010002_004\",\"growth_board1_id\":13205101,\"growth_board2_id\":13205201,\"growth_board3_id\":13205301,\"growth_board4_id\":13205401,\"growth_board5_id\":13205501,\"growth_board6_id\":13205601,\"growth_board7_id\":13205701,\"growth_board8_id\":13205801,\"growth_board9_id\":13205901,\"hit\":0,\"model_id\":1020005,\"name\":{\"ja\":\"アマテラス\",\"en\":\"Amaterasu\",\"ko\":\"아마테라스\",\"zh_hant\":\"天照大神\"},\"obtain_route_flags\":0,\"party_skill_id\":37,\"party_skill_level_id\":2,\"party_skill_type\":5,\"personality_id\":5,\"profile\":{\"ja\":\"高天原を治めるアマテラスが岩戸に身を隠せば世界は闇に包まれ、姿を現せば光に包まれる。彼女は世界を照らす太陽そのものなのだ。\",\"en\":\"Amaterasu, ruler of the heavens, hides within her cave to plunge the world into darkness, then reappears to bathe it in light. She is the literal embodiment of the sun shining down on the world.\",\"ko\":\"타카마가하라를 다스리는 아마테라스가 바위 동굴에 몸을 숨기면 세상은 어둠에 휩싸이고 모습을 드러내면 빛에 휩싸인다. 그녀는 세상을 비추는 태양 그 자체다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"統治著高天原的天照大神，一躲到岩戶之中世界就遭黑暗籠罩，一現身則光芒普照。她正是照耀世間的太陽。\"},\"publish