d\":13201701,\"growth_board8_id\":13201801,\"growth_board9_id\":13201901,\"hit\":0,\"model_id\":1050006,\"name\":{\"ja\":\"アマテラス\",\"en\":\"Amaterasu\",\"ko\":\"아마테라스\",\"zh_hant\":\"天照大神\"},\"obtain_route_flags\":0,\"party_skill_id\":21,\"party_skill_level_id\":2,\"party_skill_type\":5,\"personality_id\":1,\"profile\":{\"ja\":\"アマテラスは全ての闇を打ち祓う太陽神であり、高天原の民を統べる最高神。そんな彼女は、民と家族との間で悩み苦しむのであった。『オープンキャンパス記念公演』より\",\"en\":\"Amaterasu is the sun goddess who rules over all the inhabitants of Takamagahara, and rids the world of darkness with her light. Even she had troubles with her subjects and her family. An excerpt from \\\"Founding Day Celebration Performance.\\\"\",\"ko\":\"아마테라스는 모든 어둠을 내쫓는 태양신이며, 타카마가하라의 백성을 다스리는 최고신. 그런 그녀는, 백성과 가족 사이에서 괴로워하고 있었다. [오픈 캠퍼스 기념 공연]에서.\",\"zh_hant\":\"天照大神為能將一切黑暗驅除的太陽神，同時也為統率高天原的至高之神。那樣的她，卻被人民與家族之事所苦。取自『校園開放紀念公演』\"},\"published_at\":1571641200,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":34050,\"trait_id\":24,\"win_sequence_id\":1004,\"_id_\":1050006},\"1050007\":{\"attack_type\":2,\"attribute_id\":4,\"auto_skill1_id\":22415,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":2,\"auto_skill2_id\":12153,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":1,\"auto_skill3_id\":22522,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":2,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":242,\"base_atk\":306,\"base_hp\":1901,\"base_mdef\":131,\"base_pdef\":92,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":105,\"command_skill1_id\":4382,\"command_skill2_id\":4383,\"command_skill3_id\":4384,\"command_unique_skill_id\":4385,\"confusion_skill_id\":4386,\"cost\":15,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":3990,\"delta_atk\":5050,\"delta_hp\":62640,\"delta_mdef\":2160,\"delta_pdef\":1520,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"全体的に高いステータスを持つ。高確率でストップを付与するクライマックスACTが強力。オートスキルで自身に起死回生を付与する。\",\"en\":\"Has powerful stats. Her Climax Act has a high change at applying Stop. Her Auto Skill applies Revive to self.\",\"ko\":\"전체적으로 높은 스테이터스를 가졌다. 높은 확률로 스톱을 부여하는 클라이맥스 ACT가 강력하다. 자동 스킬로 자신에게 기사회생을 부여한다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"整體能力值都很高。強力的CLIMAX ACT有高機率賦予敵人停止效果。自動技能可賦予自己起死回生。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":1050007,\"dress_type\":0,\"entry_skill_id\":0,\"eva\":0,\"friendship10_reward_adventure_id\":0,\"friendship15_levelup_adventure_id\":3110500071,\"friendship25_reward_adventure_id\":0,\"friendship30_levelup_adventure_id\":3110500072,\"friendship_pattern_id\":134,\"get_message\":{\"ja\":\"完成された秩序と摂理。\\nここが――『世界』！\",\"en\":\"A place with absolute order and natural law—this is the \\\"World\\\"!\",\"ko\":\"완성된 질서와 섭리.\\n여기가―― [세계]!\",\"zh_hant\":\"已被完善規劃的秩序與真理。\\n這裡就是――『世界』！\"},\"get_voice\":\"v21010002_004\",\"growth_board1_id\":13204101,\"growth_board2_id\":13204201,\"growth_board3_id\":13204301,\"growth_board4_id\":13204401,\"growth_board5_id\":13204501,\"growth_board6_id\":13204601,\"growth_board7_id\":13204701,\"growth_board8_id\":13204801,\"growth_board9_id\":13204901,\"hit\":0,\"model_id\":1050007,\"name\":{\"ja\":\"世界\",\"en\":\"World\",\"ko\":\"세계\",\"zh_hant\":\"世界\"},\"obtain_route_flags\":0,\"party_skill_id\":156,\"party_skill_level_id\":2,\"party_skill_type\":5,\"personality_id\":4,\"profile\":{\"ja\":\"そして『星の少女』は楽園に至る。\\nここまでの道程、様々な出会いと別れ、たどり着いた真実と、舞台。\\n「ここが、世界だ」宙に響くその声に、最後の幕が上がる。\\n――『劇フェス』戯曲・第六幕より\",\"en\":\"And thus \\\"Star Girl\\\" goes to the promised paradise after many encounters, farewells—to arrive to the truth, and the stage. \\\"This is the world.\\\"—the last curtain rises when the voice echoes from the cosmos. From \\\"Performance Festival\\\" Play - Act 6.\",\"ko\":\"그리고 [별의 소녀]는 낙원에 도착한다.\\n지금까지의 여정, 여러 만남들과 작별하고 도달한 진실과 무대.\\n[여기가 세계다] 우주에 울려퍼지는 그 목소리에 마지막 막이 오른다.\\n――[극페스] 희곡 제6막에서\",\"zh_hant\":\"而後，『星之少女』抵達了樂園。\\n路程中歷經了各式各樣的相遇與離別，最終抵達真實與舞台。\\n「這裡是世界」伴隨著空中響起的話語，最終帷幕即將升起。\\n――取自『戲劇慶典』戲碼・第六幕\"},\"published_at\":1630422000,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":34050,\"trait_id\":47,\"win_seq