13102801,\"growth_board9_id\":13102901,\"hit\":0,\"model_id\":1050008,\"name\":{\"ja\":\"スサノオ\",\"en\":\"Susanowo\",\"ko\":\"스사노오\",\"zh_hant\":\"須佐之男\"},\"obtain_route_flags\":0,\"party_skill_id\":22,\"party_skill_level_id\":2,\"party_skill_type\":5,\"personality_id\":2,\"profile\":{\"ja\":\"ツクヨミ、アマテラスと共にヒツキの国を守護する神。豪放磊落な性格だが、姉想いで優しい一面も持つ。姉アマテラスと喧嘩別れしたことを今でも悔いている。\\n演目『高天原の巫女』より\",\"en\":\"Like his sisters Tsukuyomi and Amaterasu he also protects Hitsuki's land. Bold and open-minded, but also kind toward his sisters. He still regrets parting from Amaterasu after a fight. An excerpt from the play, \\\"Takamagahara Priestesses.\\\"\",\"ko\":\"츠쿠요미, 아마테라스와 함께 히츠키의 나라를 수호하는 신. 기개가 있고 도량이 넓은 성격이지만, 누나를 위하는 상냥한 일면도 가지고 있다. 누나 아마테라스와 싸우고 헤어진 것을 지금도 후회하고 있다.\\n작품 [타카마가하라의 무녀]에서\",\"zh_hant\":\"與月讀、天照同為守護日月國家之神。性格豪放不羈，但也有為姐姐著想的一面。與姐姐天照吵架後感到十分後悔。\\n摘自戲碼『高天原的巫女』\"},\"published_at\":1577804400,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":34050,\"trait_id\":35,\"win_sequence_id\":1116,\"_id_\":1050008},\"1050009\":{\"attack_type\":1,\"attribute_id\":2,\"auto_skill1_id\":10019,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":1,\"auto_skill2_id\":28040,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":2,\"auto_skill3_id\":10146,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":1,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":186,\"base_atk\":234,\"base_hp\":1207,\"base_mdef\":90,\"base_pdef\":137,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":105,\"command_skill1_id\":1685,\"command_skill2_id\":1686,\"command_skill3_id\":1687,\"command_unique_skill_id\":1688,\"confusion_skill_id\":1689,\"cost\":12,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":3070,\"delta_atk\":3860,\"delta_hp\":39780,\"delta_mdef\":1500,\"delta_pdef\":2260,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"クライマックスACTで前から3体の敵にダメージを与え、ACT1を封印。チャレンジレヴューで円卓の証（トリスタン）と交換ができる。\",\"en\":\"Her Climax Act damages 3 front enemies and inflicts Seal Act 1. Round Table Proofs (Tristan) can be obtained through Challenge Revues.\",\"ko\":\"클라이맥스 ACT로 앞에서부터 3명의 적에게 대미지를 가하고, ACT1을 봉인. 챌린지 레뷰에서 원탁의 증표(트리스탄)와 교환할 수 있다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"CLIMAX ACT可對前方的3個敵人進行攻擊，並封印其ACT1。使用挑戰Revue中獲得的圓桌之証（崔斯坦）即可交換獲得。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":1050009,\"dress_type\":1,\"entry_skill_id\":0,\"eva\":0,\"friendship10_reward_adventure_id\":3010500091,\"friendship15_levelup_adventure_id\":3110500091,\"friendship25_reward_adventure_id\":3010500092,\"friendship30_levelup_adventure_id\":3110500092,\"friendship_pattern_id\":132,\"get_message\":{\"ja\":\"愛と悲しみの騎士トリスタン\\n悲壮の復讐劇の始まりです\",\"en\":\"Tristan, a knight of romance and grief. This is the start of a tragic revenge drama.\",\"ko\":\"사랑과 슬픔의 기사 트리스탄\\n비장한 복수극이 시작됩니다\",\"zh_hant\":\"愛與悲傷的騎士崔斯坦\\n悲壯的復仇劇即將開始\"},\"get_voice\":\"v21010002_004\",\"growth_board1_id\":13102101,\"growth_board2_id\":13102201,\"growth_board3_id\":13102301,\"growth_board4_id\":13102401,\"growth_board5_id\":13102501,\"growth_board6_id\":13102601,\"growth_board7_id\":13102701,\"growth_board8_id\":13102801,\"growth_board9_id\":13102901,\"hit\":0,\"model_id\":1050009,\"name\":{\"ja\":\"トリスタン\",\"en\":\"Tristan\",\"ko\":\"트리스탄\",\"zh_hant\":\"崔斯坦\"},\"obtain_route_flags\":1,\"party_skill_id\":22,\"party_skill_level_id\":2,\"party_skill_type\":5,\"personality_id\":2,\"profile\":{\"ja\":\"円卓の騎士のひとり。かつてはアーサー王を敬愛する青年\\nだったが、最愛の人イゾルデを失ったことで一変。原因\\nとされるアーサーへ復讐を誓う悲しみの騎士となった。\\n演目『失われた聖杯』より\",\"en\":\"One of the Knights of the Round Table. A young man whom King Arthur had doted on, but it all changed when he lost his beloved Isolde. He became a sad knight who swore vengeance on Arthur whom he thought to be the cause of Isolde's death. From the play, \\\"The Lost Holy Grail.\\\"\",\"ko\":\"원탁의 기사 중 한 명. 한때 아서 왕을 경애하는 청년\\n이었으나, 가장 사랑하는 사람 이졸데를 잃고 변했다. 원인\\n으로 여겨지는 아서에 대한 복수를 맹세하고 슬픔을 안은 기사가 되었다.\\n작품 [잃어버린 성배]에서\",\"zh_hant\":\"圓桌騎士的其中一員。曾經受亞瑟王敬愛的青年，\\n但在失去至愛之人伊索德後卻性格大變，\\n成為了發誓向亞瑟王復仇的悲傷騎士。\\n取自戲碼『失去的聖杯』\"},\"published_at\":15