斐の虎』の異名をもつ稀代の軍略家として知られ、戦国最強の騎馬隊を率い各地を転戦した。\\n上杉謙信とは１２年に及ぶ川中島の戦いを繰り広げた。\\n演目『戦国英雄伝』より。\",\"en\":\"19th Head of the Kai Takeda clan. Known as the \\\"Tiger of Kai\\\" for his strategic prowess, he led his cavalry to several fronts. He fought against Uesugi Kenshin for 12 years in what became known as the Battles of Kawanakajima. From \\\"Sengoku Legend.\\\"\",\"ko\":\"카이 타케다 가문 19대 당주.\\n[카이의 호랑이]라는 별명을 가진 희대의 전략가로 알려졌으며, 전국시대 최강의 기마대를 이끌고 각지를 전전했다.\\n우에스기 겐신과는 12년에 걸쳐 카와나카지마 전투를 벌였다.\\n작품 [전국시대 영웅전]에서.\",\"zh_hant\":\"甲斐武田家第19代當家。\\n擁有『甲斐之虎』這個別稱，因其舉世無雙的軍師身分聞名，曾率領著戰國最強的騎馬隊征戰各地。\\n更曾與上衫謙信展開過長達12年的川中島之戰。\\n取自戲碼『戰國英雄傳』\"},\"published_at\":1627052400,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":35050,\"trait_id\":23,\"win_sequence_id\":3050,\"_id_\":1050018},\"1050019\":{\"attack_type\":2,\"attribute_id\":3,\"auto_skill1_id\":22765,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":2,\"auto_skill2_id\":22766,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":2,\"auto_skill3_id\":22767,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":2,\"auto_skill4_id\":12234,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill4_type\":1,\"base_agi\":430,\"base_atk\":748,\"base_hp\":14848,\"base_mdef\":990,\"base_pdef\":480,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":105,\"command_skill1_id\":6072,\"command_skill2_id\":6073,\"command_skill3_id\":6074,\"command_unique_skill_id\":6075,\"confusion_skill_id\":6076,\"cost\":20,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":4014,\"delta_atk\":4950,\"delta_hp\":77000,\"delta_mdef\":3300,\"delta_pdef\":2520,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"開幕時に敵役全体の継続マイナス効果耐性を解除し、AP増加を付与する舞台少女。味方全体に解除不可の不倒＆キラめき回復100と、舞台効果3種の舞台効果を付与できるクライマックスACTが強力。\",\"en\":\"Inflicts Dispel Cont. Neg. Effects Resistance and AP Up to all enemies at start. Her Climax Act applies Unremovable Resilience and Brilliance Recovery 100 to all allies, and 3 types of Stage Effects.\",\"ko\":\"개막 시에 적 전체의 지속 마이너스 효과 저항을 해제, AP 증가를 부여하는 무대소녀. 아군