\":\"The Teumessian fox's destiny was to torment people. It was like a divine curse. But she ran and lived using her cunning nonetheless. Her goal or her destiny were of no concern to her. From \\\"Chasing Sirius.\\\"\",\"ko\":\"인간들을 괴롭히라는 명을 받은 테우메소스의 여우. 그것은 마치 신의 저주 같은 존재. 그러나 여우는 자유롭게 달리며 교활하게 살아간다. 운명도 역할도 상관없다. 작품 [쫓고 쫓기는 시리우스]에서\",\"zh_hant\":\"奉命讓人們身陷苦難的透墨索斯惡狐，牠的存在就像是神給予的詛咒一般。儘管如此，狐狸還是自由地奔馳，狡猾地生存著。和命運什麼的都毫無關係。摘自戲碼『無盡追逐的天狼星』\"},\"published_at\":1574406000,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":24050,\"trait_id\":14,\"win_sequence_id\":1043,\"_id_\":1080007},\"1080008\":{\"attack_type\":2,\"attribute_id\":5,\"auto_skill1_id\":20023,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":2,\"auto_skill2_id\":20024,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":2,\"auto_skill3_id\":20023,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":2,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":177,\"base_atk\":161,\"base_hp\":1370,\"base_mdef\":132,\"base_pdef\":58,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":108,\"command_skill1_id\":2146,\"command_skill2_id\":2147,\"command_skill3_id\":2148,\"command_unique_skill_id\":2149,\"confusion_skill_id\":2150,\"cost\":12,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":2930,\"delta_atk\":2660,\"delta_hp\":45120,\"delta_mdef\":2180,\"delta_pdef\":960,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"バランスの良いステータス。敵全体にターゲット固定を付与し、自身に通常ダメージ反射と特殊ダメージ反射を付与するクライマックスACTが強力。\",\"en\":\"Has balanced stats. Her Climax Act inflicts Aggro on all enemies, and applies Reflect Normal Damage & Reflect Special Damage to self.\",\"ko\":\"밸런스가 좋은 스테이터스. 적 전체에게 타깃 고정을 부여, 자신에게 일반 대미지 반사와 특수 대미지 반사를 부여하는 강력한 클라이맥스 ACT를 가지고 있다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"擁有絕佳平衡的能力值。CLIMAX ACT可賦予所有敵人目標鎖定，並賦予自身反射普通傷害和反射特殊傷害。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":1080008,\"dress_type\":0,\"entry_skill_id\":0,\"eva\":0,\"friendship10_reward_adventure_id\":3010800081,\"friendship15_levelup_adventure_id\":31