13202601,\"growth_board7_id\":13202701,\"growth_board8_id\":13202801,\"growth_board9_id\":13202901,\"hit\":0,\"model_id\":2030006,\"name\":{\"ja\":\"酒呑童子\",\"en\":\"Shuten-doji\",\"ko\":\"슈텐도지\",\"zh_hant\":\"酒吞童子\"},\"obtain_route_flags\":0,\"party_skill_id\":22,\"party_skill_level_id\":2,\"party_skill_type\":5,\"personality_id\":2,\"profile\":{\"ja\":\"大江山に棲まう鬼。多くの手下を従えており、彼らを使って都より多くの姫君を攫っている。そんな風に勝手気ままに振る舞う酒呑童子のもとへ、ある日宿をとらせてほしいと山伏が尋ねてくるのだが……\",\"en\":\"An oni that lives on Mt. Oe. He commanded a large group of oni who would abduct young women from the capital. One day a yamabushi asked the proud oni-king to stay over the night and...\",\"ko\":\"오오에산에 사는 오니. 많은 부하를 거느리고, 그들을 이용해 도읍에서 많은 아가씨들을 납치하고 있다. 그렇게 제멋대로 행동하는 슈텐도지에게 어느 날, 잠시 머물게 해달라며 한 수행자가 찾아오는데...\",\"zh_hant\":\"棲息在大江山的鬼。擁有眾多手下，酒吞使役他們來掠奪多名位於都內的女性。這樣作風大膽隨興的酒吞童子，有天有位修行僧前來詢問他是否能夠借宿……\"},\"published_at\":1570777200,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":34050,\"trait_id\":15,\"win_sequence_id\":951,\"_id_\":2030006},\"2030007\":{\"attack_type\":1,\"attribute_id\":5,\"auto_skill1_id\":20023,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":2,\"auto_skill2_id\":10015,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":1,\"auto_skill3_id\":10076,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":1,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":187,\"base_atk\":186,\"base_hp\":865,\"base_mdef\":48,\"base_pdef\":75,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":203,\"command_skill1_id\":1631,\"command_skill2_id\":1632,\"command_skill3_id\":1633,\"command_unique_skill_id\":1634,\"confusion_skill_id\":1635,\"cost\":12,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":3080,\"delta_atk\":3060,\"delta_hp\":28490,\"delta_mdef\":790,\"delta_pdef\":1230,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"高いACTパワーを持つ。ランダムに対象を選択し、一定確率で暗闇を付与する特殊なクライマックスACTを所持。敵役が複数でも単体でもカバーできる。\",\"en\":\"Possesses high Act Power. Has a special Climax Act that targe