ear among the people – a man learns medicine to face this enemy. However, the enemy isn't only the disease. The High Priestess admonishes him that \\\"only God can save mankind.\\\" From \\\"Performance Festival\\\" Play - Act 1.\",\"ko\":\"사람들을 공포에 빠뜨리는 돌림병. 남자는 의술을 배워 이 무서운 적에 맞선다.\\n하지만 적은 병뿐만이 아니었다.\\n[인간을 구하는 것은 신의 기적뿐]이라며 여교황이 기사단을 보낸 것이다.\\n――[극페스] 희곡・제1막에서\",\"zh_hant\":\"使人們陷入恐慌的傳染病正在蔓延。但男人卻憑藉自己的醫術、挺身對抗這令人恐懼的敵人。然而他所面對的敵人卻並非僅有疾病。堅信能拯救世人的唯有神之奇蹟的女教皇向騎士團下達了追捕男人的命令。\\n——取自『戲劇慶典』戲碼・第一幕\"},\"published_at\":1611730800,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":35050,\"trait_id\":13,\"win_sequence_id\":2257,\"_id_\":2040004},\"2040005\":{\"attack_type\":1,\"attribute_id\":7,\"auto_skill1_id\":20024,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":2,\"auto_skill2_id\":10018,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":1,\"auto_skill3_id\":10076,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":1,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":177,\"base_atk\":173,\"base_hp\":1098,\"base_mdef\":66,\"base_pdef\":66,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":204,\"command_skill1_id\":1007,\"command_skill2_id\":1008,\"command_skill3_id\":1009,\"command_unique_skill_id\":1010,\"confusion_skill_id\":1011,\"cost\":12,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":2930,\"delta_atk\":2860,\"delta_hp\":36180,\"delta_mdef\":1080,\"delta_pdef\":1100,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"一番後ろの敵役にダメージを与え、凍結を付与するクライマックスACTを所持。イベント「重なる刃 忍伝・鬼紅」でユニット全体の能力を向上させる。\",\"en\":\"Her Climax Act deals damage to the enemy furthest in the back while applying Freeze. Boosts the capabilities of the entire unit in the Tales of Onikurenai event.\",\"ko\":\"가장 뒤에 있는 악역에게 대미지를 주고, 동결을 부여하는 클라이맥스 ACT를 보유하고 있다. 이벤트 「맞닿은 칼날 닌자전・오니쿠레나이」에서 유닛 전체의 능력을 향상시킨다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"擁有能給予最後面的敵方傷害，並賦予凍結的CLIMAX ACT。在活動「重疊的刀刃 忍傳・鬼紅」中能夠提升團隊全體的能力。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":2040005,\"dress_type\":0,\"entry_skill_i