ixote de la Mancha and sets out as a knight-errant astride the haggard mount Rocinante to right the world's wrongs.\",\"ko\":\"기사도 소설을 좋아하는 지방 귀족은 스스로를 돈키호테 데 라만차라고 부르기로 했다. 자기 소유의 당나귀 로시난테를 데리고 편력 기사로서 부정을 바로잡는 모험을 떠났다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"沉迷於騎士文學的沒落貴族，自稱是來自曼查的騎士吉訶德大人。他帶著自家的老馬羅西南特遊歷各地，踏上了打抱不平的騎士冒險旅途。\"},\"published_at\":1548140400,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":21050,\"trait_id\":35,\"win_sequence_id\":517,\"_id_\":3020003},\"3020004\":{\"attack_type\":2,\"attribute_id\":5,\"auto_skill1_id\":10019,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":1,\"auto_skill2_id\":20024,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":2,\"auto_skill3_id\":10076,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":1,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":150,\"base_atk\":154,\"base_hp\":1171,\"base_mdef\":76,\"base_pdef\":76,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":302,\"command_skill1_id\":1017,\"command_skill2_id\":1018,\"command_skill3_id\":1019,\"command_unique_skill_id\":1020,\"confusion_skill_id\":1021,\"cost\":12,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":2480,\"delta_atk\":2540,\"delta_hp\":38590,\"delta_mdef\":1260,\"delta_pdef\":1250,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"バランスの良いステータス。毒状態の敵役に大ダメージを与えるクライマックスACTを所持。毒を付与する舞台少女とユニットを組むとより力を発揮する。\",\"en\":\"Has balanced stats. Has a Climax Act that deals massive damage to enemies afflicted with Poison. Works great with Stage Girls that inflict Poison.\",\"ko\":\"밸런스가 좋은 스테이터스. 독 상태인 악역에게 큰 대미지를 주는 클라이맥스 ACT를 보유하고 있다. 독을 부여하는 무대소녀와 유닛을 짜면 더 큰 힘을 발휘한다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"擁有絕佳平衡的能力值。她的CLIMAX ACT可給予中毒的敵方強大的傷害。將她與可賦予中毒狀態的舞台少女編組在一起可更加發揮她的能力。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":3020004,\"dress_type\":0,\"entry_skill_id\":0,\"eva\":0,\"friendship10_reward_adventure_id\":3030200041,\"friendship15_levelup_adventure_id\":3130200041,\"friendship25_reward_adventure_id\":3030200042,\"friendship30_levelup_adventure_id\":3130200042