s formed, and thus the stars were ruled by the \\\"Emperor\\\". Still...they rebelled. Not even an absolute ruler could stop them from singing of freedom and standing on the stage. From \\\"Performance Festival\\\" Play - Act 5.\",\"ko\":\"이로써 항은하제국이 세워지고 별들은 [황제]의 것이 되었다. 하지만... 하지만 그녀들은 반항한다. 설령 상대가 절대지배자라 해도 자유를 노래하며 무대에 서기 위해.\\n――[극페스] 희곡・제5막에서\",\"zh_hant\":\"恆銀河帝國已然成立，繁星也歸『皇帝』所有。即使如此……她們仍要反抗到底。儘管對手是絕對的支配者，她們仍會為了能踏上舞台、高歌自由而戰。\\n——取自『戲劇慶典』戲碼・第五幕\"},\"published_at\":1637218800,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":11020,\"trait_id\":1,\"win_sequence_id\":3449,\"_id_\":4010015},\"4010017\":{\"attack_type\":2,\"attribute_id\":4,\"auto_skill1_id\":22525,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":2,\"auto_skill2_id\":22689,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":2,\"auto_skill3_id\":22577,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":2,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":200,\"base_atk\":324,\"base_hp\":2524,\"base_mdef\":224,\"base_pdef\":100,\"base_rarity\":4,\"chara_id\":401,\"command_skill1_id\":5300,\"command_skill2_id\":5301,\"command_skill3_id\":5302,\"command_unique_skill_id\":5303,\"confusion_skill_id\":5304,\"cost\":15,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":3850,\"delta_atk\":4824,\"delta_hp\":55324,\"delta_mdef\":2524,\"delta_pdef\":1500,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"自身に起死回生を2回付与し、敵役に錯乱を付与し、舞台の味方側に舞台効果「百花繚乱」を付与できるクライマックスACTが強力。\",\"en\":\"Her Climax Act applies Revive to self 2 times, inflicts Daze to her enemies and applies the Stage Effect [Blooming Flowers] to her allies' stage.\",\"ko\":\"자신에게 기사회생을 2회 부여하고 적에게 착란을 부여, 아군 쪽 무대에 무대 효과 [백화요란]을 부여할 수 있는 클라이맥스 ACT가 강력하다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"強力的CLIMAX ACT可賦予自身起死回生2次，賦予敵方錯亂效果，並賦予我方的舞台舞台效果「百花繚亂」。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":4010017,\"dress_type\":0,\"entry_skill_id\":0,\"eva\":0,\"friendship10_reward_adventure_id\":3040100171,\"friendship15_levelup