",\"en\":\"Siegfeld Institute of Music Acting Department, 1st Year\\nAn exchange student from China, where she won acclaim since her days as a child star. While she admires Akira, she also works hard to overtake her someday. Also likes fortune-telling.\",\"ko\":\"시크펠트 음악학원 무대배우학과 1학년.\\n중국에서 온 유학생. 고향에서는 아역 시절부터 이름을 날리던 무대소녀. 선배를 극진하게 생각하는 한편, 뛰어넘어야 할 벽으로서 아키라를 강하게 의식하고 있다. 점을 치는 것을 좋아하기도.\",\"zh_hant\":\"席格菲特音樂學院 舞台演員學科1年級。\\n從中國來的留學生，在故鄉是個從童星時代就遠近馳名的舞台少女。很憧憬學姊們，但內心也強烈覺得晶是道應該跨越的高牆。喜歡占卜。\"},\"published_at\":1540105200,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":0,\"role_index\":12050,\"trait_id\":0,\"win_sequence_id\":373,\"_id_\":4030001},\"4030002\":{\"attack_type\":1,\"attribute_id\":1,\"auto_skill1_id\":10001,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":1,\"auto_skill2_id\":10131,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":1,\"auto_skill3_id\":10150,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":1,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":147,\"base_atk\":135,\"base_hp\":856,\"base_mdef\":76,\"base_pdef\":50,\"base_rarity\":3,\"chara_id\":403,\"command_skill1_id\":249,\"command_skill2_id\":250,\"command_skill3_id\":251,\"command_unique_skill_id\":252,\"confusion_skill_id\":253,\"cost\":9,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":2440,\"delta_atk\":2230,\"delta_hp\":28200,\"delta_mdef\":1280,\"delta_pdef\":840,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"高いACTパワーを持ち、ダメージを与えるのが得意。火傷を付与するACTを2つ所持している。火傷の持続ダメージで敵役を追い込んでいこう。\",\"en\":\"Possesses high Act Power and is skilled at dishing out damage. Has two Acts that inflict Burn. Use sustained Burn damage to reduce enemy HP.\",\"ko\":\"높은 ACT 파워를 갖고 있으며 대미지를 가하는 것이 특기. 화상을 부여하는 ACT를 2개 보유하고 있다. 화상 지속 대미지로 악역을 궁지로 몰아넣자.\",\"zh_hant\":\"擁有很高的ACT力量，擅長造成傷害。具有2個能讓敵方陷入燒傷的ACT，用燒傷造成的持續傷害逼退敵方吧。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":4030002,\"dress_type\":0,\"entry_skill_id\":0,\"eva\":0,\"friendship10_reward_adventure_id\":30