みに人の懐に入り込む大胆不敵な者の正体は、世間を騒がせる怪盗、アルセーヌ・ルパンだ。\",\"en\":\"A self-proclaimed aristocrat who at times claims to be a detective or even an adventurer, the master thief Arsene Lupin hides behind myriad disguises and a silver tongue.\",\"ko\":\"스스로를 귀족이라 소개하며 때로는 탐정 때로는 모험가라며 큰소리친다. 다양한 모습과 탁월한 말솜씨로 남의 재물을 가로채는 대담무쌍한 자의 정체는 세상을 떠들썩하게 한 괴도, 아르센 루팡이다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"他雖自稱貴族，有時又以偵探或冒險家自居。這個遊走在多重身分之間，能言善道又為人所愛的無法無天之徒的真面目就是名震天下的怪盜亞森･羅蘋。\"},\"published_at\":1554044400,\"rarity_up_cost_id\":1,\"remake_cost_id\":1,\"role_index\":34050,\"trait_id\":8,\"win_sequence_id\":616,\"_id_\":4050004},\"4050005\":{\"attack_type\":1,\"attribute_id\":6,\"auto_skill1_id\":10002,\"auto_skill1_release_rank\":1,\"auto_skill1_type\":1,\"auto_skill2_id\":10008,\"auto_skill2_release_rank\":4,\"auto_skill2_type\":1,\"auto_skill3_id\":10082,\"auto_skill3_release_panel_number\":5,\"auto_skill3_release_rank\":9,\"auto_skill3_type\":1,\"auto_skill4_id\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_panel_number\":0,\"auto_skill4_release_rank\":0,\"auto_skill4_type\":0,\"base_agi\":152,\"base_atk\":96,\"base_hp\":955,\"base_mdef\":73,\"base_pdef\":48,\"base_rarity\":3,\"chara_id\":405,\"command_skill1_id\":992,\"command_skill2_id\":993,\"command_skill3_id\":994,\"command_unique_skill_id\":995,\"confusion_skill_id\":996,\"cost\":9,\"cri\":50,\"delta_agi\":2520,\"delta_atk\":1590,\"delta_hp\":31470,\"delta_mdef\":1240,\"delta_pdef\":800,\"description\":{\"ja\":\"みんなの回復役。舞台少女のHPを回復するACTを複数持つ。イベント「シークフェルト総合病院 高貴なる処方せん」でユニット全体の能力を向上させる。\",\"en\":\"The Unit's healer. Has multiple Acts that restore Stage Girls' HP. Boosts the capabilities of the entire Unit in the Siegfeld General Hospital High-Class Prescription event.\",\"ko\":\"모두를 회복시키는 역할. 무대소녀의 HP를 회복시키는 ACT를 여럿 가졌다. 이벤트 「시크펠트 종합병원 고귀한 처방전」에서 유닛 전체의 능력을 향상시킨다.\",\"zh_hant\":\"大家的回復角色，擁有複數個能夠回復舞台少女HP的ACT。在活動「席格菲特綜合醫院 高貴處方箋」中能夠提升團隊全體的能力。\"},\"dex\":5,\"dress_episode_id\":4050005,\"dress_type\":0,\"entry_skill_id\":0,\"eva\":0,\"friendship10_reward_adventure_id\":3040500051,\"friends